{"tid":1815163,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疑藏鎅刀雷射槍遭起訴 16歲男生今獲撤控","createTime":"2020-01-07T10:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T15:46:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"76608ab3dc4a91f662622b803714d60447219cc5","tid":1815163,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"市民於去年11月2日在中環皇后像廣場及遮打花園分別發起「和理摺紙鶴」及「美國人權法案集氣大會」活動，其間一名16歲男生被指在現場附近藏有鎅刀及雷射槍，被控管有攻擊性武器罪。惟案件今在東區裁判法院再度提訊時，控方以證據不足為由，申請撤銷起訴。<br />\n<br />\n原本被控的王姓男生散庭後由母親陪同，到法庭會計部取回500元保釋金。他對獲撤控一事不欲多說，只謂「終於放下心頭大石」。<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上表示，經過調查後決定撤控，但未有透露箇中原因。檢控官在庭外只稱，這是警察與律政司的共同決定。<br />\n<br />\n王姓被告原本被控於去年11月2日在中環畢打街與干諾道中交界管有一把鎅刀及雷射槍，意圖將其作非法用途使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200107/60459965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200107%2F60459965&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=82646ede\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200107%2F60459965&h=8e082d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200107/60459965</a>"},{"pid":"f3c2f4761b61ea5e2aae66c4e1f80476464c7fa8","tid":1815163,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d120ec09dd83afb41b6da4ef78037abe097929db","tid":1815163,"uid":27882,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"雷射槍?邊款?star war嗰隻定gundam嗰支?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9d51eb222ffd0f9abae89450258029141a1ba5","tid":1815163,"uid":317385,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d120ec09dd83afb41b6da4ef78037abe097929db","tid":1815163,"uid":27882,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"雷射槍?邊款?star war嗰隻定gundam嗰支?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"最好笑，佢哋竟然唔拉埋販賣「雷射槍」嘅軍火商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講撚到個雷射筆係雷射槍，講撚到好撚危險咁"},{"pid":"8c5a626f8840d33a2024174d4007e2f4d75f9978","tid":1815163,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf153f77dd1edff6290311584d5fa20db7b613a6","tid":1815163,"uid":321345,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔該煲返大呢啲新聞<br />\n冇理由俾佢高調咁拉人, 然後低調咁放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723417af2a9ec3da508ba94ff11e647e891f9642","tid":1815163,"uid":42729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0d3695fc564d2ceae4c88e7febc4820143df3ed","tid":1815163,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"基本上你唔認罪就唔會告得入"},{"pid":"c2a89bad2da3b74d68b534d041c30b60f27fd749","tid":1815163,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28777eecd6a383cd8b40b9eaf12d1af2d237d9fa","tid":1815163,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cbc82213c05d8dbe56d98e5640526f7dfe0441","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"佢好彩呀<br />\n<br />\n如果DOJ梗硬告, 遇到陳碧橋呢D<br />\n二語不說就判佢有罪入男童院"},{"pid":"2bc44ea6640e5427377e13ec6bd4c733536b8ace","tid":1815163,"uid":135276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"呢D 有冇辨法反告番佢地, 亂鳩咁黎"},{"pid":"054183ebe3bddf3e7fa70b2aaaedd85824dc7a0c","tid":1815163,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2cbc82213c05d8dbe56d98e5640526f7dfe0441","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"佢好彩呀<br />\n<br />\n如果DOJ梗硬告, 遇到陳碧橋呢D<br />\n二語不說就判佢有罪入男童院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"但依家係控方以證據不足為由，申請撤銷起訴。<br />\n紅官釘官都唔會做到野啊?"},{"pid":"4fdf01051f9977d4559bbf43d0715b255efc164d","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"大家都仲未明, D裁判官仲離譜過DOJ<br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n民主黨北區區議員與網民日前在上水合辦「和理行」集會及遊行，冀港府正視區內水貨客問題，事件中4名青年，包括去年在「光復上水」遊行中，曾疑因逃避警員而跨出天橋欄杆險墮橋的科大生，分別被落案起訴管有攻擊性武器、在公眾地方作擾亂秩序行為等4罪。今午分兩案在粉嶺裁判法院提訊，控方申請押後案件至下月18日及3月3日，以待律政司法律意見及進一步調查，期間三人獲准保釋，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中五男生另涉去年「929全球反極權大遊行」，裁判官以擔心他不依期歸押及重犯等理由，拒絕其保釋申請。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n20歲學生吳念聰被控於今年1月5日在港鐵粉嶺站外管有攻擊性武器，即一把鎅刀。中五男學生陳航生（20歲）被控於同日在上水中心地下近交通銀行<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">管有一罐紅色噴漆</span></span></strong>，意圖將其作非法用途使用。廚師江浩倫（19歲）則被控於同日在港鐵上水站外近行人過路處，煽惑他人衝擊警察防線。科大四年級生吳睿康（21歲）另被控同日在上水中心外管有攻擊性武器，即一把生果刀、一枝木棍及一把扳手。<br />\n<br />\n控方反對陳保釋，透露18年來港定居的他，於當日下午4時疑衝入上水廣場被擒獲，遭帶往港鐵上水站外搜身，警方搜獲手套、眼罩、防毒面具等。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官蘇文隆批出保釋令，各人須交出5000元擔保金、不得離港、居於報稱地址、守每晚宵禁令，另外江及吳須禁足上水四個商場及整個石湖墟範圍。"},{"pid":"fc81c99e56a07341209a8493a55c073f8159edb3","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"054183ebe3bddf3e7fa70b2aaaedd85824dc7a0c","tid":1815163,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2cbc82213c05d8dbe56d98e5640526f7dfe0441","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"佢好彩呀<br />\n<br />\n如果DOJ梗硬告, 遇到陳碧橋呢D<br />\n二語不說就判佢有罪入男童院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"但依家係控方以證據不足為由，申請撤銷起訴。<br />\n紅官釘官都唔會做到野啊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"識唔識「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果</span></span>DOJ梗硬告」呢句？"},{"pid":"c72c255c57947a4d3df5c25becceeb9d1e5c89ab","tid":1815163,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"但係點解之前有電射筆又入到罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b5dfbbb108055ebad43c5881304ea97cc15539","tid":1815163,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"雷射槍...戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d4d5fbbdc9dbee71872ed16bd8c03063c4d406","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c72c255c57947a4d3df5c25becceeb9d1e5c89ab","tid":1815163,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"但係點解之前有電射筆又入到罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"呢單係無告到, 即係無去到裁判官手<br />\n<br />\n如果強行告, 去到裁判官手<br />\n<br />\n依家班裁判官乜嘢都「警察係誠實可靠證人」、「被告作供唔可信」<br />\n<br />\n唔理三七二十一, 全部都判有罪<br />\n<br />\n去到裁判官手, 仲危險過同DOJ交手<br />\n<br />\n依家知道乜嘢叫三權合作未？"},{"pid":"a50fd0a505e8e4369c30fedcd8d5445e2aa71279","tid":1815163,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"主要係如果保釋緊又有第2單<br />\n一定比doj鋤"},{"pid":"eae20bd76288e652d8dea2abcd00394d58dfd764","tid":1815163,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b719ea2d8e69da2558e471dd3ba1a7f2d7ef0c52","tid":1815163,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"推 全亞洲最優秀警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d935b222af5bb800e64b08cfa30ed8d2b4a5a8a","tid":1815163,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2cbc82213c05d8dbe56d98e5640526f7dfe0441","tid":1815163,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"佢好彩呀<br />\n<br />\n如果DOJ梗硬告, 遇到陳碧橋呢D<br />\n二語不說就判佢有罪入男童院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"應該係律政司遇唔到紅官，費事判無罪成為案例"},{"pid":"8fe02fc986533aaa4f516841c963f1068cb37fff","tid":1815163,"uid":106675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"高震動鎅刀、陽電子雷射鎗"},{"pid":"87376aa8d1cf3599e8f61440e59a9bce2eb8a4ff","tid":1815163,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/38/29/28/3829282173e9014f